Description: pip2nix
        =======
        
        Generate nix expressions for Python packages.
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/johbo/pip2nix.svg?branch=master
           :target: https://travis-ci.org/johbo/pip2nix
           :alt: Build Status
        
